snippet: Second-round winners at the Australian Open included Novak Djokovic, Maria Sharapova and Venus Williams. Ninth-seeded Samantha Stosur, the top Australian, continued to struggle at home.
lead_paragraph: Second-round winners at the Australian Open included Novak Djokovic, Maria Sharapova and Venus Williams. Ninth-seeded Samantha Stosur, the top Australian, continued to struggle at home.

headline.main: Easy Wins for Djokovic and Sharapova, but Stosur Loses
